{"tid":1944371,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】特朗普棄用「中國病毒」　稱不後悔字眼　蓬佩奧以「武漢病毒」稱呼","createTime":"2020-03-26T10:32:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T11:45:32.000Z","uid":125193,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e6f3f878733008725ab5a7e713a3b5cdda50cfce","tid":1944371,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T10:32:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E6%A3%84%E7%94%A8-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92-%E7%A8%B1%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%8C%E6%82%94%E5%AD%97%E7%9C%BC-%E8%93%AC%E4%BD%A9%E5%A5%A7%E4%BB%A5-%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92-%E7%A8%B1%E5%91%BC/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E6%25A3%2584%25E7%2594%25A8-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%25AF%2592-%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25BE%258C%25E6%2582%2594%25E5%25AD%2597%25E7%259C%25BC-%25E8%2593%25AC%25E4%25BD%25A9%25E5%25A5%25A7%25E4%25BB%25A5-%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%25AF%2592-%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E5%2591%25BC%2F&d=NMuDHS38lj0XaiXuPCYWR5mjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=b1117c5d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E6%25A3%2584%25E7%2594%25A8-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%25AF%2592-%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25BE%258C%25E6%2582%2594%25E5%25AD%2597%25E7%259C%25BC-%25E8%2593%25AC%25E4%25BD%25A9%25E5%25A5%25A7%25E4%25BB%25A5-%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%25AF%2592-%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E5%2591%25BC%2F&h=8dcd976c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E6%A3%84%E7%94%A8-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92-%E7%A8%B1%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%8C%E6%82%94%E5%AD%97%E7%9C%BC-%E8%93%AC%E4%BD%A9%E5%A5%A7%E4%BB%A5-%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92-%E7%A8%B1%E5%91%BC/</a>"},{"pid":"53f8ebd02e538a17098f9e3404312b1cf3c89d51","tid":1944371,"uid":125193,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T10:34:17.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普表示，不會再以「中國病毒」（Chinese Virus）稱呼新型冠狀病毒，而國務卿國務卿蓬佩奧（Mike Pompeo）在七國集團外長會議後則繼續用「武漢病毒」稱號，導致七國外長會議未能發表聯合聲明。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在接受 Fox News&nbsp;訪問時說，沒有後悔用過「中國病毒」這個詞，因為是中國抹黑美國軍方在先：「他們（中國）說我們美軍是故意的，這是幹嘛？」<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">「大家都知道病毒來自中國。不過，我決定不再鬧大，我已經把事情鬧得蠻大，我想大家都清楚明白了。這完全因為他們先指控美軍，美軍是清白的。」</span></strong><br />\n特朗普又指，伊波拉（Ebola virus）和萊姆病（Lyme disease）都是以發現地點命名，這並不稀奇。不過他重申，跟國家主席習近平關係很好，又說中國這次很慘，經歷很多困難，死了數千人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n廣告<br />\n<br />\n國務卿蓬佩奧在一個發布會上說：「現在不是互相指責的時候，現在是大家合力解決全球問題的時候」，不過，他仍然以「武漢病毒」稱號。<br />\n七大工業國外長舉行視像會議，蓬佩奧說，美國希望與其他國家，包括中國合作，找出解決疫情的方法，挽救生命，「並重振遭武漢病毒（Wuhan Virus）打擊的經濟」。又說，但七國集團成員國都非常關注中共散播假消息，企圖誤導真相。ABC News&nbsp;引述兩個消息來指，七國外長在視像會議後並無發表聯合聲明，是因為蓬佩奧堅持在聲明中用「武漢病毒」這個詞，其他六國反對。"},{"pid":"df8e74bb9a0bd0353a829a040bce2d7e8d2eb7b0","tid":1944371,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T10:34:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"207544baef9ecaed5bfa842cecbb1a4de868c5a8","tid":1944371,"uid":55441,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T10:35:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8adb61d4575197fc3153867e7fda820f74980380","tid":1944371,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{